name: Or
description: Or, comprised of 70 percent indica genetics, is an Israeli strain from the medical cannabis supplier Tikun Olam. Primarily designed for patients with sleep disorders, Or also remedies an array of other symptoms including nausea, pain, inflammation, indigestion, and appetite loss.
